NANDEDKAR PARTH

library("EBImage")
#
image.col <- readImage("obama.png")
#
image.gs <- apply(imageData(image.col), c(1,2), mean)
#
#
A <- matrix(image.gs,256,256)#A

#
res.svd=svd(A,nu=30,nv=30)
U <- res.svd$u
V <- res.svd$v
D <- diag(res.svd$d)
D20 = D[1:30,1:30]

##===========================================
low.image <- U%*%D20%*%t(V) #
#
display(image.gs)

display(low.image)
